title: Unfazed and surprisingly alert: Imran Khan warns of threats to Pakistan's democracy
description: Imran Khan was very uncertain he'd make it out of the High Court on Friday night, even after he'd been bailed for two weeks.

title: Ukraine comes under Russian missile fire during Eurovision
description: Ukraine came under fire from Russian missiles during the Eurovision Song Contest.

title: Erdogan seeks to fire up his supporters as a divisive election draws near
description: After twenty years of running his country, Recep Tayyip Erdogan was hardly going to change tack now.

title: Poland detects balloon 'from Belarus' in its airspace
description: Poland says it has detected what appears to be an observation balloon in its airspace that flew in from the direction of Belarus.

title: Anger as 'tasteless' ice cream stand set up in front of Auschwitz
description: An ice cream stand set up outside Auschwitz has been described as "tasteless" and "disrespectful" by managers of the historic site.

title: Pakistan's former prime minister Imran Khan says country's democracy at 'an all-time low'
description: Imran Khan has claimed democracy in Pakistan is at "an all-time low" in an exclusive interview with Sky News.

title: 'Selfish, egotistical' young Italians should have more children instead of pets, Pope says
description: "Selfish, egotistical" young Italians should have more children and fewer pets, the Pope has told a conference of pro-family organisations in Rome.

title: 'One of world's oldest lions' killed after preying on livestock
description: A 19-year-old male lion, believed to be one of the oldest in the world, was killed after trying to take livestock from a community in Kenya.
